Consolidated Edison, Inc., or ConEdison, Inc. is an energy company which provides energy-related products and services through the following subsidiaries: Con Edison Solutions, Con Edison Energy, ConEdison Development, Con Edison of New York, and Orange and Rockland Utilities. The company… MoreConsolidated Edison, Inc., or ConEdison, Inc. is an energy company which provides energy-related products and services through the following subsidiaries: Con Edison Solutions, Con Edison Energy, ConEdison Development, Con Edison of New York, and Orange and Rockland Utilities. The company is 180 years old. Consolidated Edison Company of New York serves New York City (except for an area in Queens) and Westchester County, NY. The company also provides gas services for Manhattan, the Bronx and some areas of Queens and Westchester County. In addition, Consolidated Edison, Inc has the largest steam system in the world, and services most of Manhattan.
